Economic Freedom Fighters (EFF)  leader Julius Malema, has sent a strong warning to the US to stay away from South Africa’s domestic issues. This follows US President Donald Trump’s Tweet  Thursday morning on South Africa’s land policy where he asked his Secretary of State to study the country’s land seizures and expropriations as well as farm killings.  His Tweet was based on a Fox News insert that erroneously claimed that President Cyril Ramaphosa had begun seizing land without compensation.   Malema says the issue of land in South Africa is an emotive issue . For more watch below: 